text.tspan: Average usual weekly hours worked, women 15 years and older,
Average usual weekly hours worked on the main job, for women ages 15+. Estimates correspond to total declared employment.
This includes part-time and full-time employment, as well as self-employment and dependent employment.
Data source: OECD Labor Force Statistics (2017)
